INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(2, 1, '2011-06-14 18:36:19', '2011-06-14 18:36:19', '[full]\r\n\r\nAHD International, LLC a unique team of individuals with extensive experience in all areas of nutritional products industry. Since its inception, AHD International has grown dramatically and continues to increase its global customer base of manufacturers, wholesalers, and distributors. We supply the highest quality nutritional products in raw material powders and oils. Our low prices and quick delivery satisfy customers across North America. We specialize in acting as agents for major foreign manufacturers by distributing nutritional ingredients in North America.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>You''ll find that our sophisticated capabilities of supplying raw materials, ingredients, powders, oils, and natural extracts can give you a strong advantage in the marketplace</strong></em>\r\n\r\nWe can help you compete more successfully, because we specialize in new and hard-to-find raw materials, up and coming products, and natural materials that are in demand.\r\n\r\n[/full]\r\n\r\n[section_header]A Little More About Us[/section_header]\r\n\r\n[one_third]\r\n<h3><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-75" title="customer-satisfaction-294x120" src="http://localhost:8888/AHD/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/customer-satisfaction-294x120.jpg" alt="" width="294" height="120" /></h3>\r\n<h3>High Customer Satisfaction</h3>\r\nOur customer list covers some of the largest most respected companies in the world; as well as numerous, fast growing businesses, that count on AHD month after month. In fact, 80% to 90% of our customers continue to do business with us.\r\n\r\n[/one_third]\r\n\r\n[one_third]\r\n<h3><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-81" title="quality-standards-294x120" src="http://localhost:8888/AHD/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/quality-standards-294x1201.jpg" alt="" width="294" height="120" /></h3>\r\n<h3>Quality Standards</h3>\r\nWe work with some of the finest and most respected independent testing laboratories. And we have our own triple-check system to help ensure that customer products are evaluated for natural purity, consistency, and exceptional quality.\r\n\r\n[/one_third]\r\n\r\n[one_third_last space=yes]\r\n<h3><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-83" title="worldwide-delivery-294x120" src="http://localhost:8888/AHD/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/worldwide-delivery-294x1201.jpg" alt="" width="294" height="120" /></h3>\r\n<h3>Fast Delivery</h3>\r\nYou''ll find that, on average, we meet or exceed our customer''s delivery deadlines 95% of the time. That''s critical when you need to get products to the market quickly.\r\n\r\n[/one_third_last]\r\n\r\n[one_half]\r\n<h3>Specialized Representatives</h3>\r\nOur representatives are knowledgeable, skilled, and customer oriented-enthusiastic reps who know how to resource products. Count on them to search out the best materials, suggest ideas for keeping costs under control, and recommend some of the best testing, processing, and storage facilities for your special requirements.\r\n<h3><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;">[/one_half]</span></h3>\r\n[one_half_last space=yes]\r\n<h3>America-Based, World Reach</h3>\r\nAHD is concerened with providing our customers with excellent products and customer service; we are not part of a large, impersonal corporation. Headquartered in Atlanta, Georgia USA, our representatives travel worldwide to search for the finest raw materials with the highest beneficial characteristics. You''ll benefit from our global perspective, our industry contacts, and our full range of service options.\r\n\r\n[/one_half_last]\r\n', 'About AHD', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about', '', '', '2011-08-31 18:17:47', '2011-08-31 18:17:47', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/AHD/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(91, 1, '2011-08-31 14:51:58', '2011-08-31 14:51:58', 'LuraLean™ (Propol Mannan) is the satiety-support ingredient that helps maintain post-meal GI and cholesterol levels already within the normal range.* It has the highest molecular weight in the natural world.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[section_header]The LuraLean Mechanism[/section_header]\r\n\r\n[one_third]\r\n<h4>LuraLean Mechanism 1</h4>\r\n0 Calorie pure fiber stomach filler Satiety support* Swells and expands to 200 times the original weight\r\n\r\n[/one_third]\r\n\r\n[one_third]\r\n<h4>LuraLean Mechanism 2</h4>\r\nFood moves slowly in the body* Prolonged satiety* Operates most effectively in the stomach and the intestines*\r\n\r\n[/one_third]\r\n\r\n[one_third_last space=yes]\r\n<h4>LuraLean Mechanism 3</h4>\r\nOil absorbing property* Fat trapping magnet* Oils/fats are trapped in the hydrated layer to be carried out of the body*\r\n\r\n[/one_third_last]\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/AHD/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/stock-photo-beautiful-japanese-green-park-in-summer-time-70382437.jpg"><img class="size-medium wp-image-110 alignleft" title="LuraLean" src="http://localhost:8888/AHD/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/stock-photo-beautiful-japanese-green-park-in-summer-time-70382437-300x223.jpg" alt="Natural LuraLean" width="300" height="223" /></a>\r\n\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n<h4>Over 60 International Clinical Studies &amp; 14 Safety Studies</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Regulates appetite*</li>\r\n	<li>Regulates extra calorie absorption*</li>\r\n	<li>Regulates cholesterol absorption*</li>\r\n	<li>Improves metabolism*</li>\r\n	<li>Delays gastric emptying time*</li>\r\n	<li>Supports intestinal health</li>\r\n	<li>Helps maintain a healthy immune response*</li>\r\n	<li>High temperature tolerance</li>\r\n	<li>Salt, sugar and pH stable</li>\r\n	<li>Non-binding with minerals/vitamins</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>[/one_half_last]</div>\r\n<h4>Registration Status for LuraLean™</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>FDA - GRAS Food Chemicals Codex</li>\r\n	<li>Official Functional Food Ingredient (Japan)</li>\r\n	<li>Food/Food Additive (Japan)</li>\r\n	<li>Food Ingredient with Health Claim (Russia)</li>\r\n	<li>Joint FAO/WHO Expert Committee on Food Additives</li>\r\n	<li>Natural Health Product (Canada) u E-number (EU)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Assured Clinical Performances</h4>\r\nOver 100 clinical studies worldwide including:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Supports immune system*</li>\r\n	<li>Relief of occational constipation*</li>\r\n	<li>Helps maintain cholesterol levels already within the normal range*</li>\r\n	<li>Weight Reduction*</li>\r\n	<li>Body Fat Reduction*</li>\r\n	<li>Probiotics*</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nStudy subjects include obese children and pregnant women\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n[one_half]\r\n\r\n<img class="size-full wp-image-127 alignleft" title="luralean-weightloss-2xDaily" src="http://localhost:8888/AHD/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/luralean-weightloss-2xDaily.png" alt="Weight Loss, Twice Daily" width="350" height="221" />[/one_half]\r\n\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/AHD/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/luralean-weightloss-3xDaily.png"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-128" title="luralean-weightloss-3xDaily" src="http://localhost:8888/AHD/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/luralean-weightloss-3xDaily.png" alt="Weight Loss, 3 Times Daily" width="350" height="221" /></a>\r\n\r\n[/one_half_last]\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n<h4>Patented Technology</h4>\r\nLuralean™ is obtained via a specialized 3 stage purification process. The manufacturing of LuraLean™ is patented (33 countries) by Shimuzu Chemical Corporation, Japan. Many other applications and technologies are patented and patent filed in USA, EU, Japan and Central/South American countries.\r\n[/one_half_last]', 'LuraLean', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'luralean', '', '', '2011-09-01 18:43:17', '2011-09-01 18:43:17', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/AHD/?post_type=product&#038;p=91', 0, 'product', '', 0);
