INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(150, 1, '2011-09-01 19:34:41', '2011-09-01 19:34:41', 'AHD and their partnering company Fytexia® presents a new active ingredient unolex®, a dry extract of Mangosteen (Garcinia mangostana L.) dosed at 10% in alphamangostin. Scientifically proven in double blind placebo controlled study, unolex® reduces joint pain in seniors (-50%) and athletes (-31%).\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[section_header]The Benefits of Unolex[/section_header]\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/AHD/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/unolex-chart-1.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-135 alignleft" title="unolex-chart-1" src="http://localhost:8888/AHD/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/unolex-chart-1.png" alt="Unolex Chart" width="179" height="245" /></a>[two_thirds]\r\n\r\nunolex® reacts on cyclooxygenase COX2. The production of COX2 is induced by cytokines, main actors in the inflammatory response, when it detects an intrusion. COX2 is responsible for Prostaglandin production PGE2, an essential factor of the physiological inflammation response. unolex®, thanks to its alpha-mangostin composition, directly inhibits the cytokins action, decreasing the production of cycloxygenase, and therefore the effects of an inflammatory reaction.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Helps maintain joint health</li>\r\n	<li>Prevents Tendinitis</li>\r\n	<li>Prevents Rhumatisms</li>\r\n	<li>Prevents Arthrosis</li>\r\n	<li>Aids seniors &amp; athletes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>[/two_thirds]</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4>Human Clinical Study:</h4>\r\n22 patients (athletes; seniors) 600mg a day of MangoSelect®. We observed a significant decrease of joint pain after one week treatment.\r\n<h4>Animal Clinical Study:</h4>\r\n85 mg of Unolex® significantly decreases inflammatory reaction induced by lipopolysaccharides (LPS) in animals.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Unolex', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '134-revision-14', '', '', '2011-09-01 19:34:41', '2011-09-01 19:34:41', '', 134, 'http://localhost:8888/AHD/134-revision-14', 0, 'revision', '', 0